Kerala Market Price Analysis Dashboard
Objective

The objective of this project is to analyze Kerala’s commodity market pricing trends using Power BI.
The dashboard provides insights into:

Price variation across markets (Min, Max, Modal Price)

Commodity-level price trends over time

Market distribution and commodity contribution

Price stability (Volatility %)

Top-performing commodities based on average price
It helps traders, farmers, analysts, and government agencies understand pricing behavior and market patterns.

Dataset

Source: Kerala Market Sales Data (CSV file provided)

Number of Rows: ~146,900

Number of Columns: 10

Key Columns:

State

District

Market

Commodity

Variety

Grade

Arrival_Date

Min_Price

Max_Price

Modal_Price

